{"id": 2618, "genre": 1001, "title": "作为一个成年人，你都用什么结界来保证自己不被打扰？", "description": "戴上耳机，生人勿近。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Bellott）", "record_count": 3230, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181108103624GB2v8XCI9g3HAseV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-12T04:55:01Z", "options": [{"id": 310272, "content": "不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202842}, {"id": 311296, "content": "耳机+克鲁泽同款", "image": "img/option/option/20181116113348aJA7kqsTDfhGxWev", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222905}, {"id": 310273, "content": "游戏世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448127}, {"id": 310529, "content": "假装耳机里好大声音", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501469}, {"id": 310274, "content": "随时随地戴耳机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486712}, {"id": 310276, "content": "耳机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234981}, {"id": 313092, "content": "手机没电也要带耳机，摘了近视眼镜装看不见，戴口罩，戴帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511894}, {"id": 310277, "content": "一直假装发消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381822}, {"id": 312837, "content": "冷漠脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512099}, {"id": 310278, "content": "耳机啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250694}, {"id": 310279, "content": "最好的当然是一副耳机🎧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489516}, {"id": 312073, "content": "我出门不带耳机大概会疯掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345390}, {"id": 310283, "content": "一张无欲无求的厌世脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500541}, {"id": 310796, "content": "交谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502835}, {"id": 311564, "content": "看手机/假装看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505873}, {"id": 313100, "content": "急匆匆的脚步", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514606}, {"id": 314124, "content": "面无表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821543}, {"id": 310285, "content": "一张别人欠我五百万没还的臭脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922109}, {"id": 310542, "content": "在家不出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441768}, {"id": 310798, "content": "高冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502839}, {"id": 310287, "content": "免打扰模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500510}, {"id": 310288, "content": "我喜欢同性👀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497063}, {"id": 310289, "content": "当然是管住自己的嘴啦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500564}, {"id": 310291, "content": "冷漠的态度和疏离感", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484183}, {"id": 310293, "content": "尴尬而不失礼貌的微笑～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500569}, {"id": 310294, "content": "关闭微信朋友圈！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493444}, {"id": 310551, "content": "冷漠脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501564}, {"id": 310296, "content": "自带结界，一直活在自己的世界里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500576}, {"id": 310808, "content": "如果戴面具 可以的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487397}, {"id": 310297, "content": "冷漠", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43355}, {"id": 310298, "content": "口罩+帽子 谁都看不见我的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497629}, {"id": 310810, "content": "不对视。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495913}, {"id": 310302, "content": "带上耳机，撸代码！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1491367}, {"id": 310560, "content": "早睡晚起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475025}, {"id": 315681, "content": "当我不想被打扰时身边总有：看不完的一页书，写不完的一页纸，刷不完的手机桌面，突然别过去的头，间接性失聪，间接性失明，间接性失语等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 310307, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 310308, "content": "足不出户。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372466}, {"id": 310564, "content": "戴上帽沿大的帽子，再插上耳机，下雨天还有伞，天冷了还有口罩，齐活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497849}, {"id": 310309, "content": "保持一种我很忙的状态，无论是手机，电脑或者纠紧眉头思考状，都可以让对方闭嘴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493233}, {"id": 310310, "content": "丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333322}, {"id": 310311, "content": "严谨的作息和看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484475}, {"id": 310567, "content": "床帘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494876}, {"id": 310312, "content": "啦啦啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437007}, {"id": 310313, "content": "本身就不会被打扰啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261099}, {"id": 310314, "content": "降噪耳机 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142509}, {"id": 310315, "content": "像高仓健一样把领子竖起来😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212802}, {"id": 310316, "content": "对于不满意不喜欢的事情总是沉默以对\n如果硬要评论，一般都说“还好吧”“一般”“还可以”…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500114}, {"id": 311596, "content": "靠脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779866}, {"id": 310317, "content": "玩游戏呀，他山是他山，我自流污水，哈哈哈哈～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500628}, {"id": 310318, "content": "坐角落背靠墙带耳机看电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499877}]}